The paper deals with sentiment analysis of citations in scientific documents, which involves natural language processing and machine learning techniques. Therefore, it is likely to belong to the sub-categories of Computational Linguistics (cs.CL), Information Retrieval (cs.IR), Machine Learning (cs.LG), Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI), and Deep Learning (cs.DL).
